Apko koi bhi kaam krne se pehle apko Goals pata honay chahiye.

Abraham Lincoln said, "A goal properly set is halfway reached."

How to set the Goal?

Apne ap se pucho 
What do  you want to do in life ?
Why do  you want to do in life ?
Can you do that ?

Yeh teeno sawaal ka answer hai agar pas toh apke pas maqsad mojood mil jaeyga.

Agar ap confuse hai kaafi career fields ko lekar toh mentor se baat krein jo un fields ke mahir hai or unse us cheez ki advantages or disadvantages puchein.

Ab dekhein gaye SMART goals 
S -- Specific
M -- Measurable
A -- Achievable
R -- Realistic
T -- Timely

*Apne ameer bnna hai yeh specific nahi hai lekin ap amount batyein gaye apne kitna ameer banna hai Tou yeh specific hai(But measurable nahi hai.) 

*Measurable nahi hai ,kya apne yeh bataya kay jo bhi amount apne earn krni hai woh kitne arse mein apne earn krni hai means 1st year mein kitna krna hai dusre saal mein kitna krna hai and so on.

*Achievable ,isko is tareeke se smjhain kay ap ke pas specific amount or measurable time period hai pr apke pas dimagh hai ap khud se sochain kay kya yeh achievable hai .Like ap yeh kehte hai ap agle 5 saal mein America ke President bnay gaye .Specific bhi hai Measurable bhi hai lekin Achievable nahi hai.

*Realistic Goal rkhna hai .

*Timely means apne apko challenge dein time bound ke havalay se kay yeh kaam mein itne time period mein krunga.

What Not to do while setting the Goal ?

*Goals without Plan
*Vague Goals
*Goals to please others or Inspire from others
*Forced Goals

How to Achieve the Goals ?

* Set Goals That Motivate you
* Set SMART Goals
* Write Your Goals (Meaning ache tareeke se likhay or chotay chotay plans banayein)
* Furious Optimism (Achi Umeed)
* Laser Focused
* Embrace Failure / Stay Strong / Keep Going